  30:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_ControlVoltageScaling() and HAL_PWREx_GetVoltageRange() to
  31:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        set / get the voltage scaling range.
  32:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) Voltage scaling can be one of the following values :
  33:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) voltage output scale 1 : 1V2
  34:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                   => Used when system clock frequency is up to 160 MHz
  35:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) voltage output scale 2 : 1V1
  36:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                   => Used when system clock frequency is up to 100 MHz
  37:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) voltage output scale 3 : 1V0
  38:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                   => Used when system clock frequency is up to 50 MHz
  39:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) voltage output scale 4 : 0V9
  40:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****                   => Used when system clock frequency is up to 24 MHz
  41:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  42:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnableFastSoftStart() and HAL_PWREx_DisableFastSoftStart()
  43:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        to enable / disable the fast software startup for the current regulator.
