  45:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnterSTOP1Mode() function to enter the whole system to
  46:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        Stop 1 mode. Wake-up from Stop 1 mode could be following to an event or
  47:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        an interrupt according to low power mode intrinsic request called
  48:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (__WFI() or __WFE()). (Regulator state on U5 devices is managed
  49:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        internally but regulator parameter is kept for product compatibility).
