  53:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        an interrupt according to low power mode intrinsic request called
  54:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (__WFI() or __WFE()). (Regulator state on U5 devices is managed
