  62:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
  63:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    (#) Call HAL_PWREx_EnterSHUTDOWNMode() function to enter the whole system in
