 587:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    *** Stop 3 mode ***
 588:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****    ===================
 589:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     [..]
 590:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       The Stop 3 mode is based on the Cortex-M33 Deepsleep mode combined with
 591:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       peripheral clock gating. In Stop 3 mode, all clocks in the VCORE domain
 592:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       are stopped.
 593:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       The PLL, MSIS, MSIK, HSI16 and HSE oscillators are disabled.
 594:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       All SRAMs and register contents are preserved, but the SRAMs can be
 595:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       totally or partially switched off to further reduce consumption.
 596:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       The BOR is always available in Stop 3 mode.
 597:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
 598:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) Entry:
 599:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           The Stop 3 mode is entered by using the HAL_PWREx_EnterSTOP3Mode()
 600:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****           function.
