 732:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief  Enter the whole system to Stop 3 mode.
 733:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   Stop 3 is the lowest power mode with full retention, but the
 734:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         functional peripherals and sources of wakeup are reduced to the same
 735:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         ones than in Standby mode.
 736:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   Stop mode achieves the lowest power consumption while retaining
 737:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         the content of SRAM and registers. All clocks in the VCORE domain
 738:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         are stopped. The PLL, the MSI (MSIS and MSIK) RC, the HSI16 RC and
 739:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         the HSE crystal oscillators are disabled. The LSE or LSI is still
 740:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         running.
 741:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   The system clock when exiting from Stop mode can be either MSIS up
 742:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         to 24 MHz or HSI16, depending on software configuration.
 743:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @param  STOPEntry : Specifies if Stop mode is entered with WFI or WFE
 744:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                     instruction.
 745:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                     This parameter can be one of the following values :
 746:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                     @arg @ref PWR_STOPENTRY_WFI enter Stop mode with Wait
 747:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                               For Interrupt request.
 748:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                     @arg @ref PWR_STOPENTRY_WFE enter Stop mode with Wait
 749:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *                               For Event request.
 750:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @retval None.
 751:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   */
