1686:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       Several STM32U5 devices RAMs are configurable to keep / lose RAMs content
1687:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       during Run mode.
1688:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****        (+) Retained content RAMs in Run modes are :
