1690:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) SRAM2
1691:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****              (++) SRAM3 (available only for STM32U575xx, STM32U585xx, STM32U59xxx,
