1696:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       SRAM2 is configurable to keep / lose its content in Stop 3 and Standby
1697:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       modes. The SRAM2 retention feature granularity is at pages level.
