2370:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   This bit is used to obtain the best trade-off between low-power consumption
2371:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         and wakeup time. SRAM4 wakeup time increases the wakeup time when exiting
