2397:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /** @defgroup PWREx_Exported_Functions_Group5 I/O Pull-Up Pull-Down Configuration Functions
2398:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief    I/O pull-up / pull-down configuration functions
2399:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *
2400:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** @verbatim
2401:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****  ===============================================================================
2402:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****             ##### IO Pull-Up Pull-Down Configuration Functions #####
2403:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****  ===============================================================================
2404:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     [..]
2405:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       In Standby and Shutdown mode, pull up and pull down can be configured to
2406:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       maintain an I/O in the selected state. If the APC bit in the PWR_APCR
2407:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       register is set, the I/Os can be configured either with a pull-up through
2408:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       PWR_PUCRx registers (x=A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J), or with a pull-down through
2409:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       PWR_PDCRx registers (x=A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J)), or can be kept in analog state
2410:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       if none of the PWR_PUCRx or PWR_PDCRx register is set.
2411:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       (+) Port J is available only for STM32U59xxx, STM32U5Axxx, STM32U5Fxxx
2412:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       and STM32U5Gxxx devices.
2413:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccuB84o5.s 			page 93


2414:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****     [..]
2415:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       The pull-down configuration has highest priority over pull-up
2416:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       configuration in case both PWR_PUCRx and PWR_PDCRx are set for the same
2417:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       I/O.
2418:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       This configuration is lost when exiting the Shutdown but not from Standby
2419:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****       mode.
2420:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
2421:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** @endverbatim
