2424:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** 
2425:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c **** /**
2426:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @brief  Enable pull-up and pull-down configuration.
2427:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   When APC bit is set, the I/O pull-up and pull-down configurations
2428:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         defined in PWR_PUCRx and PWR_PDCRx registers are applied in Standby
2429:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         and Shutdown modes.
2430:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note   Pull-up set by PUy bit of PWR_PUCRx register is not activated if the
2431:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         corresponding PDy bit of PWR_PDCRx register is also set (pull-down
2432:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         configuration priority is higher). HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullUp() and
2433:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         HAL_PWREx_EnableGPIOPullDown() API's ensure there is no conflict
2434:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         when setting PUy or PDy bit.
2435:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @retval None.
2436:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   */
