2629:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  This state is effective in Standby and Shutdown modes only if APC bit
2630:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        is set through HAL_PWREx_EnablePullUpPullDownConfig() API.
