2632:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        power-on reset, maintained when exiting the Standby mode.
2633:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   * @note  To avoid any conflict at Standby and Shutdown modes exits, the
2634:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        corresponding PUy bit of PWR_PUCRx register is cleared unless it is
2635:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *        reserved.
